author: hwright
msg: Don't do forward deltification on regions of a repository that don't support
it, namely, pre-1.6 portions of a repository which has been upgraded.
(deltify_mutable): Determine if the revision we are looking at is older than
the upgrade, and optionally apply our earlier deltification process.

author: julianfoad
msg: Indent the tree conflict description in "svn info" for easier reading.

author: julianfoad
msg: Distinguish "switch" from "update" when raising a tree conflict. A follow-
up to r33673, now making the distinction actually appear.
(check_tree_conflict): Add an "edit baton" param and use it to determine
the operation kind (switch vs. update) of the conflict.
Pass the edit baton in calls to check_tree_conflict().
